        "class": "",
        "text": "and for the continual meat offering, and for the continual burnt offering; for the daily sacrifice, morning and evening, which always had a meat offering along with it, Exodus 29:38, ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and for the continual meat offering, and for the continual burnt offering; for the daily sacrifice, morning and evening, which always had a meat offering along with it, ",
