            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and for the set feasts; of passover, pentecost, and tabernacles; in which also were offered other sacrifices, besides the daily one, Numbers 28:16, ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
