        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") we find the regulations for a burnt offering, with a meal offering, morning and evening. This is what is probably intended in the present passage, in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 3:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
